AMG
========================

[ 0.3.9 ] separate SA and UA code
[ 0.5.0 ] profile and optimize a few core functions: RS, EM
[       ] profile and optimize a few core functions: SA, UA (Xiaozhe)

[ 0.8.5 ] non-overlapping/overlapping Schwarz smoother
[       ] maximal independent set based on a strength matrix (Ludmil)
[       ] replace Schwarz smoother by a C version (Xiaozhe, Ludmil, James B., Fei)
[       ] polynomial smoothers -- 1/x and Chevbshev (Xiaozhe)
[       ] Tarjan algorithm and other orderings (Xiaozhe and Ludmil)
[       ] strength matrix based on (polynomial) smoothers (Xiaozhe)
[       ] AMG based on mesh information

[ 0.9.0 ] aggressive coarsening strategies (Xiaozhe)
[ 1.5.0 ] Notay's aggregation scheme
[       ] aggregation based on MIS (Xiaozhe)
[       ] cleanup the compatible coarsening (Xiaozhe)
[       ] LAMG's aggregation scheme (Xiaozhe)

[ 0.8.6 ] standard interpolation
[       ] polynomial interpolation -- vector preserve (Xiaozhe)
[       ] multi-pass interpolation
[       ] long-distance interpolation
[       ] bootstrap interpolation

[       ] estimation of extreme eigenvalues (Xiaozhe)
[       ] smoothing interpolation by polynomial smoothers (Xiaozhe)
[       ] interpolation can preserve more kernel vectors (Xiaozhe)

